Cleaned Weather Data from Horsham and Curyo

Source: R/cleaned_weather.R
cleaned_weather.Rd

A dataset of ten-minute observation weather data from on-site weather stations at Horsham and Curyo.

cleaned_weather

Format

A data.frame with 2202 rows and 6 variables:

site

Location where trial was located

rep

Replicate number. The sequential number of rain or irrigation event for a given site

time

Date in POSIXct, format YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS

wind_speed

Recorded wind speed in metres per second

wind_direction

Recorded wind direction in compass degrees

rainfall

Recorded precipitation in millimetres

Source

Dr Joshua Fanning, AgricultureVictoria, Horsham, Vic, AUS

Contents

Developed by Ihsanul Khaliq, Joshua Fanning, Paul Melloy, Jean Galloway, Kevin Moore, Daniel Burrell, Adam H. Sparks, GRDC Project USQ1903-003RTX, Agriculture Victoria and GRDC co-investment project DAV00150, GRDC Project DJP1097-001RTX.
